  "title": "Quality Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Description</strong></p><p>The Quality Executive will be responsible to ensure compliance in SS651, ISO 9001, 18001, and 45001standards in the operations departments.</p><p> <strong>Duties: </strong></p><p>1.     Drive compliance by working closely with Business Units (Warehouse, Transportation, Depots)</p><p>2.     File & upkeep all hardcopy and softcopy documents</p><p>3.     Handle process and compliance audit inquiries in internal & external audits</p><p>4.     Participate in internal & external training to stay up to date in SS651, ISO 9001,\n18001, and 45001 standards</p><p>5.     Oversee various daily, monthly, and quarterly inspections in QEHS and account-specific regime</p><p>6.     Prepare monthly compliance report for QEHS requirements</p><p>7.     Adhere to all company rules and regulations including safety rules</p><p>8.     Any other duties and responsibilities assigned from time to time</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>1.     Diploma holders in Engineering or Business or possess relevant certification in QESH</p><p>2.     Possess good knowledge in SS651, ISO9001, 18001 and 45001 standards</p><p>3.     Minimum 2 years’ experiences in QESH management system and auditing</p><p>4.     Able to analyse issues with problem solving and root cause analysis tools</p><p>5.     Good communication skills and able to liaise with internal and external stakeholders effectively </p><p><strong>Others Information: </strong></p><p>1.     Work on alternate Saturday</p><p>2.     2 ways transport from Jurong East MRT</p><p>3.     Daily meal subsidy</p><p>4.     In-house gym </p><p>5.     Dental, medical, insurance benefits</p>",
